# This folder is committed as a portable, OFFLINE "backup / basis" bundle:
# the standalone Python runtimes (python/) and the full wheel cache (wheels/)
# ARE tracked on purpose, so the worker can be rebuilt anywhere with no
# internet straight from a checkout.
#
# Only TARGET-GENERATED, machine-specific build outputs are excluded below —
# install.bat / install.sh recreate them on each machine, and they must NOT be
# committed: a venv bakes absolute drive/mount paths (broken if moved), and
# runtime/ is just python/*.tar.gz unpacked (redundant with the archive).
.venv-win/
.venv-linux/
runtime/
